  <div class="scenario">
    <div class="scenario__text">
      <div class="inner">
        <h2>Scenario</h2>
        <p>
          When crashed or blocked mountain climbers must be rescued by helicopter, mountain rescuers and doctors are flown to the immovable climbers to prepare the injured for evacuation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Attached to a 30 to 60 meter long rope the rescuer is flown close to the rock wall. This maneuver is a difficult task even under good weather conditions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <img
      data-sizes="auto"
      src="/images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-100.jpg"
      data-srcset="
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-100.jpg 100w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-200.jpg 200w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-400.jpg 400w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-600.jpg 600w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-800.jpg 800w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-1200.jpg 1200w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-1500.jpg 1500w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-2000.jpg 2000w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/scenario-2500.jpg 2500w
      "
      class="lazyload scenario__img blur"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="problem">
    <h2>The Problem</h2>
    <p>
      The rescuer has almost no control over his position. The movement of the heliopter is transfered to the person with a delay. The rotation around the rope is caused by random oscillation and the downwash of the helicopter.
    </p>
    <p>
      If the rescuer is swinging with his back to the wall,  holding on to the rock wall is more difficult and the rescuer can get hurt.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="idea">
    <img
      data-sizes="auto"
      src="/images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-100.jpg"
      data-srcset="
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-100.jpg 100w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-200.jpg 200w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-400.jpg 400w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-600.jpg 600w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-800.jpg 800w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-1200.jpg 1200w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-1500.jpg 1500w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-2000.jpg 2000w,
        /images-responsive/rotation-control/idea-2500.jpg 2500w
      "
      class="lazyload blur"
    />
    <div class="text">
      <div class="inner">
        <h3 class="title-top">My Idea</h3>
        <h2 class="title-bottom">GYROSCOPE</h2>
        <p>
          To enable the rescuer to align himself with the rock wall, a battery-powered flywheel is attached between the rescuer and the rope. The rapid rotation of the flywheel produces a resistance in free space. The rescuer can use this resistance to control his position on the vertical axis.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="usage">
    <img
      data-sizes="auto"
