    <div class="visual">
      <h2>Visual Design</h2>
      <p>
        Because the users are mounted at high altitude underneath Rotation control. It should communicate a high stability when perceiving the underside.
        The overall impression should show strength to transmit the controlle it provides also visuel.
      </p>
      <p>
        This is realized by a scaffold of metal on the outside, fixed by well visible screws.
        The slightly angular appearance supports the communication of strength and solidity.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Visuele design also note the important practical aspects of space constraints, the good visibility and the ablity to easy catch it the handles.
      </p>
    </div>
